{"tid":328230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解書展個「名作家講座系列」全部係蝗語主講都無人理？","createTime":"2017-07-19T12:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T15:46:18.000Z","uid":69835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6264accb35830748669c04dd17afd0ad07bee66d","tid":328230,"uid":69835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"話說小弟心血來潮想睇下今年書展有咩講座好聽<br />\n見到個「名作家講座系列」咪諗睇下有咩名作家<br />\n點知仆你個臭街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部都寫住「此活動以普通話主講。」<br />\n你無睇錯，係全部<br />\n佢一共13個講座，全部都係用蝗語<br />\n入面17個作家，有11個係大陸人，4個台灣<br />\n得2個係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然書展仲有其他廣東話講座<br />\n但香港無名作家咩？邊可能呢個系列一大半都係大陸人<br />\n而且個班大陸作家，我相信香港人都唔係好認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傳統媒體淨係識講乜嘢人排頭位<br />\n呢啲嘢反而唔理<br />\n各位合力推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d1be239c918c0bcd3927d47975c7e5b5a05051","tid":328230,"uid":69835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"頭先仲寫咗篇文去輔仁，詳細少少<br />\n大家唔可以唔理呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/07/19/164660/%E5%90%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E8%AC%9B%E5%BA%A7%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95%E4%BB%B2%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E7%95%80%E9%A6%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F164660%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B1%2595%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E7%2595%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%2F&d=knZUuThT10lE1RgPl8n9P9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7dc01fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/07/19/164660/%E5%90%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E8%AC%9B%E5%BA%A7%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95%E4%BB%B2%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E7%95%80%E9%A6%99/</a>"},{"pid":"e45bda201c841a2baaf315df066ae45584de8bbd","tid":328230,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98d4b70332db52ffbd24502766db7ff06e7da63f","tid":328230,"uid":69835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88a166431816fcb989cfd7ee03b6a72f33553bb","tid":328230,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"冇人理架喇<br />\n<br />\n個個為左三萬蚊學店過夜而嘈餐死，簡直係雞係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e711d1f74ade8b2046a316d187d4f59d2aeeb31","tid":328230,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"真係睇書嘅邊會去書展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0da9f2d52022ad3540c1ebf92703f5b7b936a26","tid":328230,"uid":69835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係睇書嘅邊會去書展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n書展真係人多到唔啱睇書<br />\n不過有時啲唔急住睇嘅書<br />\n等入去先買又真係抵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694e19003f7ef4e961aa26d0731055b8184f8890","tid":328230,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"名作家們申請左工作簽證未？"},{"pid":"62f5a1dff97dc43a58beb9f54ecb61d915632140","tid":328230,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"文化界, 出版社最奶共架啦"},{"pid":"10e2fe9545aa8665dfe271c5feae57cd0e0da9ab","tid":328230,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"敢問而家香港有邊d比較出名既文學家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上比較叻都係大陸台灣<br />\n香港咪最多揾下d旅遊書編緝lo"},{"pid":"20cc7d566272bf63a69d98feb1c105b55a585177","tid":328230,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"881de3c83c49a594d8f1284c73f3033f0ea4a176","tid":328230,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"作家都搵唔到錢<br />\n香港邊有作家架"},{"pid":"92d4166d65b732065f234ce751527e66f1d5e531","tid":328230,"uid":69835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"新一代嘅作家實少架啦，真係難搵食<br />\n但香港一定唔係無作家到要揀晒大陸人"}]}